It's about the cultural significance

00:32.728 --> 00:35.063
- of the PEI potato.
- That's not boring?

00:35.097 --> 00:38.500
Which title do you like better?
<i>You Say Potato, I Say Identity?</i>

00:38.534 --> 00:40.201
- Oh...
- Or... or...

00:40.236 --> 00:42.704
<i>One Potato, Two Potatoes,
