To the universe!

02:58.628 --> 03:00.596
- (Andy sighs)
- To swimming with the lobsters

03:00.630 --> 03:03.131
or zip-lining or...
Two Anne of Green Gables

03:03.166 --> 03:05.567
- walking right at us.
- Oh, my God.

03:06.295 --> 03:07.970
