04:24.436 --> 04:27.605
that lean build,
that popularity with women

04:27.640 --> 04:29.707
that... I mean, I assume you have.

04:29.742 --> 04:31.910
- More or less, yeah!
- Yes.

04:31.944 --> 04:35.113
And you... You are...

04:36.146 --> 04:38.049
Creepy Ted.

04:40.187 --> 04:41.052
I'm sorry, Creepy Ted?

04:41.086 --> 04:43.121
