you haven't seen us act.

05:19.792 --> 05:22.260
Ha! Ha! Acting, um...

05:22.294 --> 05:25.396
- Acting comes from in here.
- Oh, wow. That's...

05:25.431 --> 05:28.099
I... Yeah, I feel it. I feel it.
Oh, yeah, you were...

05:28.133 --> 05:30.335
