06:29.029 --> 06:32.030
Come on, Rollie! Oh, my gosh! Rollie!

06:32.064 --> 06:34.799
- Is he OK?
- (droning beep)

06:34.833 --> 06:36.968
Um... I'm sorry, everybody...

06:37.002 --> 06:40.138
- He's gone.
- (Ruth): No!

06:40.172 --> 06:42.473
